E4Plus1.uk.description: Days of Wine and D'Oh'ses: After forgetting his birthday party, Barney quits drinking and takes helicopter flying lessons. (S11 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Perfect Pairs: Phil, Claire, Alex and Luke love looking after the twins, but find it exhausting. But then they realise that the babies might be useful for their to-do lists... (S11 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Verdict: Claire is excited about giving Haley and Alex a great time on Bring Your Daughter to Work Day, but the staff don't make it easy. Gloria is thrilled to be on jury duty. (S7 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The More You Ignore Me: Claire and Phil have their hands full when Luke gets arrested for driving without a licence, and then they catch Alex sneaking out of a liquor store. (S7 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pilot: The first ever episode of the hit sitcom. Leonard and Sheldon's geeky world is shaken up by the arrival of a beautiful new neighbour. (S1 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Big Bran Hypothesis: Sheldon sneaks into Penny's flat to tidy it. She's not happy about it. (S1 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: All eyes are on Lucas as his desperate bid to win back Dillon begins to spiral out of control. Frankie confides in Dodger, but will his concern make her question her new beau?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: The walls close in on Mercedes as she races to get the money for her blackmailer. And Dillon and Rex try to support Ste as he struggles with his emotions.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pygmoelian: After he's snubbed for a Duff beer calendar, Moe goes for plastic surgery and ends up so handsome that he becomes a soap star. (S11 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bad Fish Paradigm: Penny opens up to a reluctant Sheldon after a less-than-stellar first date with Leonard, putting him in the awkward position of having to keep a secret. (S2 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Codpiece Topology: Seeing Penny out on a date with another guy sends a distressed Leonard rushing back to Leslie Winkle, much to Sheldon's dismay. (S2 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Barbarian Sublimation: Penny becomes addicted to an online game based on the world of Conan the Barbarian and begins to pester Sheldon for advice. (S2 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Griffin Equivalency: Full of confidence after being named one of People magazine's '30 to Watch Under 30', Raj hits on Penny and becomes impossibly arrogant. (S2 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Euclid Alternative: When Leonard can't drive Sheldon to and from work, the friends stage an intervention to overcome Sheldon's fear of getting behind the wheel. (S2 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cooper-Nowitzki Theorem: Sheldon's friends are mystified when a younger student is attracted to him, and her intense devotion soon becomes too much to bear. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Panty Piata Polarization: Sheldon bans Penny from the flat for numerous minor infractions, so she retaliates. Howard and Raj search for the America's Next Top Model house. (S2 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Lizard-Spock Expansion: Howard is furious when a woman who he likes falls for Leonard, despite Howard's efforts to woo her. (S2 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The White Asparagus Triangulation: Sheldon is delighted that Leonard has finally found a girlfriend who matches up to his high standards... Perhaps a little too delighted. (S2 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Vartabedian Conundrum: Leonard goes to Penny for help when his relationship with Stephanie takes off faster than he'd like, but will he act on her advice? (S2 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bath Item Gift Hypothesis: At Christmas, Leonard's hunky colleague starts dating Penny, while Sheldon's obsession with gift-giving etiquette torments everyone. (S2 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Killer Robot Instability: Kripke challenges the boys to a robot duel, while Howard is devastated when Penny finally tells him what she thinks of his chauvinism. (S2 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Friendship Algorithm: Sheldon develops a scientific procedure for making friends when he discovers that Kripke has control of a new supercomputer at the university. (S2 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Financial Permeability: When Sheldon lends Penny some money, it brings her ex-boyfriend Kurt back into her life, with negative consequences for the gang. (S2 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Maternal Capacitance: A disastrous visit from Leonard's mother has the unexpected side-effect of bringing Leonard and Penny closer together. (S2 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cushion Saturation: A game of paintball leads to a squabble when Penny accidentally shoots paint at one of Sheldon's cushions. Romance blossoms between Howard and Leslie. (S2 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Terminator Decoupling: Leonard, Sheldon, Howard and Raj discover that beautiful sci-fi actress Summer Glau is on board their train to San Francisco. (S2 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Work Song Nanocluster: Penny's home-based business selling hair accessories gets out of hand when an overexcited Sheldon takes charge of production. (S2 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Dead Hooker Juxtaposition: Penny develops a rivalry with a sexy female neighbour who moves into the apartment building and threatens to become the 'new Penny'. (S2 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hofstadter Isotope: Leonard is devastated when Stuart from the comic book shop chats up Penny. Even worse, she doesn't mind. Sheldon tries to scupper the budding romance. (S2 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Vegas Renormalization: Leonard and Raj take a heartbroken Howard to Las Vegas, leaving Sheldon locked out of his flat and forced to stay with Penny. (S2 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Classified Materials Turbulence: Things look up for Leonard when Penny makes a surprising revelation on her second date with Stuart. Howard sees a flaw in his NASA project. (S2 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Monopolar Expedition: Leonard and Penny reconsider their feelings for each other, but then Leonard is offered the opportunity to spend the summer working at the North Pole. (S2 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Donny and Misbah's relationship is on the rocks. Frankie receives a threatening letter. And Mercedes wants to turn over a new leaf with Warren.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tale of Two Springfields: When class rivalries split Springfield in two, Homer becomes mayor of 'New Springfield'. (S12 Ep2/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Mo Farah, Motsi Mabuse, Katherine Kelly and Ben Miller make meringue roulades and traditional Italian biscuits, and render a childhood memory in cake.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: This time the Goggleboxers watch: The Celebrity Traitors, Love Is Blind, Coronation Street, The Girlfriend, Nightmares of Nature, The Reluctant Traveller and Yorkshire Air 999. (S26 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Dating Naked UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - A Devilish Twist: A three-time Miss Wales arrives, turning some of the boys' heads. And Rylan, dressed as an evil angel, delivers a hellish surprise... (S1 Ep7)

Film4.uk.description: (2021) The spy-caper franchise continues with the origins story of the Kingsman agency, as a plucky group battle an international conspiracy at the outbreak of WWI. With Ralph Fiennes.

Film4.uk.description: Tom Cruise talks about making the sci-fi-adventure Oblivion.

Film4.uk.title: Oblivion
Film4.uk.description: (2013) Sci-fi action-mystery set on a war-ravaged planet Earth that's been largely abandoned by humanity. With Tom Cruise, Andrea Riseborough, Olga Kurylenko and Morgan Freeman.

Film4.uk.description: (2022) Drama starring Emma Thompson as a recently widowed, retired teacher who has a sexual bucket list she wants to get around to now that she has the time and, perhaps, even the energy.

Film4.uk.title: Hunter Killer
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Nautical action thriller. Gerard Butler stars as an unconventional submarine skipper sent to investigate the torpedoing of a US vessel. With Gary Oldman, Linda Cardellini and Common.

Film4.uk.description: (2020) Moving drama. In the 1980s, the Yi family move to rural Arkansas to live the American Dream. But the reality is harsh and the family are soon struggling to survive. In Korean/subs.
